:<br />\n<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2019/10/05/asia/hong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F10%2F05%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL5nDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=ae04ccc5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F10%2F05%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&h=53844d7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2019/10/05/asia/hong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk/index.html</a><br />\nViolent protests which began Friday stretched into the early hours of Saturday, beyond the midnight deadline when the new anti-mask regulations began. They spread out across the city and soon devolved into violent clashes, with protesters throwing petrol bombs and police responding with pepper spray and tear gas.<br />\n<br />\nUN rights chief :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/10/06/un-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2F2019%2F10%2F06%2Fun-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence%2F&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL5nDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=f7016516\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/10/06/un-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence/</a><br />\nUN human rights chief Michelle Bachelet said Saturday she was &ldquo;troubled&rdquo; by Hong Kong&rsquo;s increasingly violent pro-democracy protests<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fm6HkAU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFm6HkAU.jpg&h=cfadcc90&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DNQQuuf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDNQQuuf.jpg&h=e8fe24d4&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dkz2kAV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdkz2kAV.jpg&h=e42958dd&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wt3FRHB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWt3FRHB.jpg&h=836cc635&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n開始無人話警察武力不對等，國際開始支持港府。再係咁落去，美國人權及民主法案好可能被否決<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以做多D外國文宣 (Twitter), 唔好覺得有班人會做, 人人都要文宣!!"},{"pid":"3eadaf7f5a62b6043322713952d229fdbb854557","tid":1631931,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:38:56.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"31af20d0073cc67d26fca98e58301480f2ff429c","tid":1631931,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"556ef1ba240daab2b02ff3e0fce6004bb670a73e","tid":1631931,"uid":135110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:16.000Z","msg":"人地都可以利用投票去帶風向"},{"pid":"ebdbc7b29ce8fccf3185c98e74aa96b8d5c0886c","tid":1631931,"uid":57566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:39.000Z","msg":"痴線 投票po先易帶風向<br />\n真相係越辯越明"},{"pid":"3f1baaf6f634d248ecce96a633aec250e0b619f3","tid":1631931,"uid":118822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"556ef1ba240daab2b02ff3e0fce6004bb670a73e","tid":1631931,"uid":135110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:16.000Z","msg":"人地都可以利用投票去帶風向"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:40:40.000Z","msg":"依家P牌無得投票 真既人仍然係主流<br />\n反之 佢地一兩個挑釁性既留言 已經可以令無心灰意冷"},{"pid":"a95431b1c3871bc5c3d187002eff47a76b19d4e9","tid":1631931,"uid":135110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f1baaf6f634d248ecce96a633aec250e0b619f3","tid":1631931,"uid":118822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"556ef1ba240daab2b02ff3e0fce6004bb670a73e","tid":1631931,"uid":135110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:16.000Z","msg":"人地都可以利用投票去帶風向"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:40:40.000Z","msg":"依家P牌無得投票 真既人仍然係主流<br />\n反之 佢地一兩個挑釁性既留言 已經可以令無心灰意冷"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:41:23.000Z","msg":"有d五毛唔係P牌"},{"pid":"3f8beb97b78207f33e6b14b8d078f38f2f8f61c6","tid":1631931,"uid":118822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a95431b1c3871bc5c3d187002eff47a76b19d4e9","tid":1631931,"uid":135110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f1baaf6f634d248ecce96a633aec250e0b619f3","tid":1631931,"uid":118822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"556ef1ba240daab2b02ff3e0fce6004bb670a73e","tid":1631931,"uid":135110,"like":0,